description:
This is a 41 minute workout called 'ENDURANCE CALORIE SHRED | 40 MIN Treadmill Workout!' from the channel IBX Running.
The workout falls under Cardio/Treadmill and Cardio/Running.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Treadmill for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Challenging and Moderate.

Original workout description: Today we are crushing a 40 Min Endurance Calorie Shred Tread workout! Let's get out there to crush it!

Join this channel to get access to perks and support the channel!
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCJumOlRn9C592ijW9sUC2Hg/join

40 minutes of run and recovery intervals

All speeds and inclines are suggestions. Please stay safe and within your comfort zone!

Join our community of runners: http://www.ibxrunning.com
Merch: https://www.ibxrunning.com/store
IBX Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/ibxrunning/
Rachael's Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/bedopefitness/
